title: Lima
description: Natural food store providing healthy and organic groceries, bento boxes to go, Japanese made vegan cookies and non-dairy ice cream, etc. Has a community table as well as a separate kitchen in the shop where cooking classes are held. Address in Japanese 東京都渋谷区代々木2-23-1.
streetAddress: 2-23-1 Yoyogi, 130 New State Manor Building, Shibuya
